title: Learn Finnish While You Sleep:Mitä kieltä sinä puhut?

media:group.media:title: Learn Finnish While You Sleep:Mitä kieltä sinä puhut?
media:group.media:description:
Learn Finnish While You Sleep:Mitä kieltä sinä puhut? What Language do you speak?
So we are going to talk about languages and how to respond to the question of what language do you speak.
In Finnish often times the name of the language is the same as the name of the country, but note the name of the language is always written with a lower case letter and the name of the country with a capital letter which is different from English
